<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>INTERNATIONAL&#174; VT 365 DIESEL ENGINE - CYLINDER HEAD AND VALVE TRAIN - Component Reassembly</stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>Component Reassembly</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="assemble" graphiccount="2">
            <title>Hydraulic Cam Follower</title>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Clean hydraulic cam followers and roller follower guide. Use care to maintain roller
                    follower identification and orientation.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>Identify orientation of each cam follower and guide during assembly.</para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
            <figure id="f2650484" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figd03/D0303.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                         scalefitheight="312px" box="no"/>
                <caption>Figure 181. Installation of cam follower in guide</caption>
            </figure>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Lubricate and place each hydraulic cam follower into its respective roller follower
                    guide.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <figure id="f2650485" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figd03/D0302.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                         scalefitheight="312px" box="no"/>
                <caption>Figure 182. Installation of cam followers and guide</caption>
            </figure>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Lubricate cam followers with clean engine oil and install followers into their
                    respective bores.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>See the "High Pressure Oil Pump" section, for procedure relating to the rear engine tube
                        assembly (branch) which mounts over the rear cam follower guides.
                    </para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install an M6 x 15 bolt with washer to roller follower guides (front guides only) and
                    torque bolt to the standard value .
                </para>
            </step1>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
